            "label": "About This Product",
            "heading": "UAE's Favourite Smoke Bubble Machine for Kids",
            "subheading": "",
            "body": "<p>The Smoke Bubble Machine for Kids produces <strong>glowing, smoke-filled bubbles every minute</strong> using completely safe water-based vapor. No soap. No sticky residue. No cleanup — just screen-free magic that kids aged 3 and up go wild for.</p><p>Unlike regular bubble wands, this machine fills each bubble with <strong>shimmering RGB LED-lit mist</strong> that floats, glows, and pops into a tiny cloud. One-button operation means even toddlers figure it out instantly — press once to start, press again to stop.</p><p><strong>Built for UAE families.</strong> Whether you are hosting a birthday party in Dubai Marina, an Eid gathering in Abu Dhabi, or a Friday afternoon at Sharjah's Al Majaz Waterfront — this bubble machine turns any space into an instant wonderland. It thrives in warm outdoor conditions and works indoors with zero mess.</p><p>The <strong>8-hour USB rechargeable battery</strong> means no mid-party shutdowns and no disposable batteries. One charge covers an entire party, a full weekend of play, or weeks of daily 30-minute sessions.</p><p><strong>Safe</strong> BPA-free ABS plastic, smooth rounded edges, non-toxic water vapor — no chemicals needed for the smoke effect. Available in Pink and Blue with identical performance.</p><p>TipTop360 delivers <strong>free next day across all 7 UAE emirates</strong> — Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ajman, Fujairah, Ras Al Khaimah, and Umm Al Quwain. Cash on Delivery available. 14-day hassle-free returns.</p>",
            "alt_bg": true
          }
